title: Help and Room Info Commands
story: dungeo
description: Test HELP, ABOUT, DIAGNOSE, and ROOM commands

---

> help
[OK: contains "HOW TO PLAY"]

> about
[OK: contains "DUNGEON"]

> diagnose
[OK: contains "perfect health"]
[OK: contains "can be killed"]

# ROOM prints the verbose room description (name + prose, no object list)
> room
[OK: contains "West of House"]
[OK: contains "open field"]

# RNAME and OBJECTS are rendered via story-defined channels (dungeo.rname /
# dungeo.objects in src/channels.ts) for the browser client only; the CLI
# main channel intentionally does not display them, so they are not tested here.
